In your microservices you need to enable CORS

That means:

@Configuration
public class CorsConfig {

    @Bean
    public WebMvcConfigurer corsConfigurer() {

        return addCorsMapping(registry) -> {
                registry.addMapping("/**")
                        .allowedOrigins("http://localhost:3000") // Adjust this to your frontend's URL
                        .allowedMethods("GET", "POST", "PUT", "DELETE", "OPTIONS")
                        .allowedHeaders("*");
        }
    }

    @Bean
    public RestTemplate restTemplate() {
        return new RestTemplate();
    }
}

Check this video for more details: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=p_D64E-HHc4

You can add fallback as well
